text:
Hi Magnus, there are a few things that you can try here.

1. Add labels to your inputs and selects. That will make your form more consistent with all other forms inside HubSpot 
2. if you really really don't want labels, wrap everything in flex component with direction flex. You can control the spacing using gap
```    // example 1
    &lt;Form&gt;
      &lt;Select label="select" /&gt;
      &lt;Input label="Input1" /&gt;
      &lt;Select label="select2" /&gt;
      &lt;Input label="Input2" /&gt;
      &lt;Input label="Input3" /&gt;
    &lt;/Form&gt;
  );```
```    // example 2
    &lt;Form&gt;
      &lt;Flex direction="column" gap="sm"&gt;
        &lt;Select /&gt;
        &lt;Input /&gt;
        &lt;Select /&gt;
        &lt;Input /&gt;
        &lt;Input /&gt;
      &lt;/Flex&gt;
    &lt;/Form&gt;```
